<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Regulation lims:pit-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:current-date="2025-07-24" lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022507" lims:id="1022507" gazette-part="II" regulation-type="SOR" xml:lang="en" xmlns:lims="http://justice.gc.ca/lims"><Identification lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022508" lims:id="1022508"><InstrumentNumber>SOR/98-337</InstrumentNumber><RegistrationDate><Date><YYYY>1998</YYYY><MM>6</MM><DD>10</DD></Date></RegistrationDate><ConsolidationDate lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22"><Date><YYYY>2025</YYYY><MM>7</MM><DD>25</DD></Date></ConsolidationDate><EnablingAuthority lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022510" lims:id="1022510"><XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="P-1">PARLIAMENT OF CANADA ACT</XRefExternal></EnablingAuthority><LongTitle lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022511" lims:id="1022511">Senate Sessional Allowance (Deductions for Non-attendance) Regulations</LongTitle></Identification><Order lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022512" lims:id="1022512"><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022513" lims:id="1022513" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="yes" list-item="no"><Text>The Senate, pursuant to section 59 of the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="P-1">Parliament of Canada Act</XRefExternal>, hereby makes the annexed <XRefExternal reference-type="regulation">Senate Sessional Allowance (Deductions for Non-attendance) Regulations</XRefExternal>.</Text></Provision><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022514" lims:id="1022514" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="yes" list-item="no"><Text>June 9, 1998</Text></Provision></Order><Body lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022515" lims:id="1022515"><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022516" lims:id="1022516" level="1"><TitleText>General</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022517" lims:id="1022517"><Label>1</Label><Text>The deduction to be made from the sessional allowance of a senator under subsection 57(1) of the <XRefExternal reference-type="act" link="P-1">Parliament of Canada Act</XRefExternal> is increased to $250 per day for every sitting day beyond twenty-one on which the senator does not attend a sitting of the Senate.</Text><HistoricalNote><HistoricalNoteSubItem lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022519" lims:id="1022519">SOR/2002-23, s. 1; err.(F), Vol. 136, No. 2</HistoricalNoteSubItem></HistoricalNote></Section><Heading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022520" lims:id="1022520" level="1"><TitleText>Coming into Force</TitleText></Heading><Section lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="1022521" lims:id="1022521"><Label>2</Label><Text>These Regulations come into force on July 1, 1998.</Text></Section></Body></Regulation>